# The move command executed successfully, indicating I am now at the new intermediate position.
# I will now attempt to move even closer to the stone patch by adjusting my position again.

# Moving to the coordinates of the nearest stone patch, which is at (-14.5, -14.5).
# This time, I will move directly to the coordinates of the stone patch.

desired_stone_position = Position(-14.5, -14.5)  # The exact position of the nearest stone patch.
move_to(desired_stone_position)  # Move to the exact position of the stone patch.
